      "content": "\"one step at a time\" sounds like something people say when they don't get it. there is no next step. there's just the debt and the fact that i failed everyone. i've spent my whole life building this and now i'm just a guy with nothing and a mountain of consequences. it feels like the world just stopped for me, but it keeps moving for everyone else. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to not have to deal with the weight of this anymore.",
